      "id": "PopularPost31682",
      "post_content": "Sigh...great-sounding card, mediocre ability.  \nThis card would still have been far from broken if the \"kicker effect\" was ![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol)![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol) only.  \nI'd have considered using it in constructed then, but for ![2](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=2&type=symbol)![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol) i can only hardly imagine an effective use.  \n[Pandemonium](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pandemonium) will do a better job most of the time.  ",
      "posted_by": "Mode",
