    {
      "id": "PopularPost34586",
      "post_content": "This card is bad. Period. Any decent burn deck would have much better firepower for much less mana. Even in limited I don't see how this is useful, as all it does it sit there for a few turns until you actually have enough mana to use it, and even then it's likely only used for a finisher, and can be replaced by a number of other much better and efficient finishers. The flavor text should've read: *Where mana cost and near-uselessness collide.*",
      "posted_by": "Omniance",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost34586\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">This card is bad. Period. Any decent burn deck would have much better firepower for much less mana. Even in limited I don't see how this is useful, as all it does it sit there for a few turns until you actually have enough mana to use it, and even then it's likely only used for a finisher, and can be replaced by a number of other much better and efficient finishers. The flavor text should've read: <i>Where mana cost and near-uselessness collide.</i></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '34586'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy8605\">Omniance</span>\r\n                                (11/9/2009 5:42:14 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftCl