      "id": "PopularPost35056",
      "post_content": "This card is underrated, it just needs to be used in conjunctoin with the right cards. Don't think Ball Lightning, Think Zektar Shrine Expedition. Hellspark Elemental works very nice to, both the first time around and on unearth, dealing an (optimal) 12 damage in conjuction with this card. Rakka Mar is another honorable mention.\n  \n   \nObviously things like Luminarch Acension and Sigl of the Empty throne work wonderfully as well.",
