      "id": "PopularPost35864",
      "post_content": "I'm new to magic so I have what might seem like a dumb question about this card. If I use this card and target a player, can that player block the damage done in any way? For example, I brought out a 5/5 creature and target Player A, Player A claims that since it is a creature doing the damage and the card says that that creature does the damage, he can block the damage with anyone of his creatures? Is that true?\n  \nAny feedback would be appreciated. Thanks. ",
      "posted_by": "Hewie",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost35864\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_post\">I'm new to magic so I have what might seem like a dumb question about this card.  If I use this card and target a player, can that player block the damage done in any way?  For example, I brought out a 5/5 creature and target Player A, Player A claims that since it is a creature doing the damage and the card says that that creature does the damage, he can block the damage with anyone of his creatures?  Is that true?  \r<br/>Any feedback would be appreciated. Thanks.  </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '35864'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy18861\">Hewie</span>\r\n                                (11/17/2009 2:02:19 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../I