    {
      "id": "PopularPost35910",
      "post_content": "Not a great constructed card. It could work in limited, but it's quite expensive - you're going to have to wait a few turns to utilise it (ie. turn 6 without missing land drops would get you 3 damage from a normal 3 CMC creature damage creature).  \n  \nIt would be \\*much\\* more playable if it was a higher initial cost and lower 'kicker' cost. 4R for the initial cost and R for the kicker would be great (perhaps a bit unbalanced), and 3R + 1R would be better and probably fairly balanced too.",
      "posted_by": "JaxsonBateman",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost35910\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">Not a great constructed card. It could work in limited, but it's quite expensive - you're going to have to wait a few turns to utilise it (ie. turn 6 without missing land drops would get you 3 damage from a normal 3 CMC creature damage creature).<br/><br/>It would be *much* more playable if it was a higher initial cost and lower 'kicker' cost. 4R for the initial cost and R for the kicker would be great (perhaps a bit unbalanced), and 3R + 1R would be better and probably fairly balanced too.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '35910'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy6928\">JaxsonBateman</span>\r\n                                (11/17/2009 8:22:20 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/Right